reactor.core

注释类型 TestLoggerExtension.Redirect


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Target(value={TYPE,METHOD})
 @ExtendWith(value=TestLoggerExtension.class)
public static @interface TestLoggerExtension.Redirect
    Set up a TestLoggerExtension that routes log messages only to the injected TestLogger, suppressing the logs from the original logger. Messages don't include thread names.
